								<wikidot:authorUserId>4058903</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The idea itself (multiple afterlives) isn't very fresh, and the &quot;unseen mysterious person who is possibly a god of some sort communicates through phone and just so happens to sound like Barb in HR&quot; bit is overdone on this site. The touch of the researcher actually making use of the afterlife selection was good, but not enough to save a tired concept. -1</p> 
				 	]]>
