					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-4288006#post-3633641</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-4288006/scp-3806#post-3633641</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2017 05:50:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ResearcherKatash</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3097260</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I really liked this one.</p> <p>Maybe it's not the longest or most developed SCP ever added to this site, but I found it really interesting.</p> <p>Great characterization of the entity, although this was quite a humorous character it fitted the article well.</p> <p>Also I liked the idea of the older gods getting together and forming some form of business, made the divine appear mundane which is a welcome relief from all of the omnipotent gods and god weapons that seem to be all too common here.</p> <p>+1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
