					<![CDATA[
						 <p>image source: <a href="https://pixabay.com/p-1059336/?no_redirect">https://pixabay.com/p-1059336/?no_redirect</a></p> <p>Thanks to my beta readers <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510811063" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" >Ihp</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/some-potato" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2341932&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510811063" alt="Some_Potato" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2341932)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/some-potato" >Some_Potato</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3208919&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510811063" alt="taylor_itkin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3208919)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" >taylor_itkin</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2156983&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510811063" alt="psul" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2156983)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" >psul</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cambrian" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3400053&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510811063" alt="Doctor Cambrian" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3400053)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cambrian" >Doctor Cambrian</a></span>, who pointed out that this bears a resemblance to <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IFe9wiDfb0E">Welcome to Life: The singularity ruined by lawyers</a>. I saw that when it first came out back in 2012, but I wasn't consciously basing this off it.</p> <p>This scip was actually inspired by the opening line of <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C25qzDhGLx8">CGP Grey's recent video</a>: &quot;Death is busy, but he can squeeze you in right now.&quot;</p> 
